item.title: Dhanesh Aradhye
item.description: Dhanesh Aradhye is software engineer, data architect and an expert in BI Analytics field. He has deep understanding and inclination towards web and mobile technologies, and has curious nature towards world finance and news affecting it. He also has an unhealthy obsession with Doctor Who, Avengers, other Marvel and many more sci-fi movies.
